{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/title.png?t=1698422416\" /><br>Terra Toy is a simple and peaceful creative sandbox where you sculpt terrain and place down objects to create the scenic planet of your dreams. There is no goal or game; Build whatever you wish simply for the beauty of it using the easy-to-use tools and extensive library of decorations.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/sculpt.png?t=1698422416\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/sculpt.gif?t=1698422416\" /><br>Sculpt and terraform the terrain, raising it to erect hills and mountains, lowering it to reveal valleys and rivers, and smoothing it to achieve a photogenic finish.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/paint.png?t=1698422416\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/paint.gif?t=1698422416\" /><br>Paint a colorful set of biomes onto the planet, creating varying environments and adding a sense of diversity and structure.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/decorate.png?t=1698422416\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/prop.gif?t=1698422416\" /><br>Place props to add detail and life to the world, choosing among many unique items to customize and plop onto the ground.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/share.png?t=1698422416\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435320/extras/share.gif?t